# coding: utf-8
'''*********************************************************
任务名称：MySQL DES 解密
功能描述：解密用 MySQL 的 DES_ENCRYPT() 函数加密过的字段，并将解密结果写入新字段。实测解密速度可达每秒 10,000 行以上。
输入表：在解密配置文件中指定（文件管理上传至 MINIO）
输出表：同输入表
创建人：zhangch2
创建时间：2024-11-06
解密配置文件样例：
```json
    {
        "connection": {                             # 数据库连接信息，需要写入权限
            "db.host": "localhost",
            "db.user": "root",
            "db.password": "xxxx",
            "db.database": "ods_prod",
            "db.port": 3306
        },
        "fields": [
            {
                "table_name": "ODS_BUS_EMPLOYEE",   # 需要解密的表名
                "unique_key": "EMP_ID",             # 表的唯一键（必须有）
                "ciphertext": "EMP_NAME",           # 被加密的列名
                "cleartext": "EMP_NAME_CLEAR",      # 解密后存放的列名
                "password": "83BCE225D9FD151A"      # 解密用的密码
            },
            {
                "table_name": "ODS_BUS_EMPLOYEE",   # 可以一次解密多个表的多个列
                "unique_key": "EMP_ID",
                "ciphertext": "MOBILE_PHONE",
                "cleartext": "MOBILE_PHONE_CLEAR",
                "password": "83BCE225D9FD151A"
            }
        ]
    }
```

修改历史：
  版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明
                2024-12-12       zhangch2           增加解密配置文件样例
*********************************************************'''

from MyDES import MyDES

mydes = MyDES("人力资源解密配置.json")
mydes.update()

/***********************************************************
任务名称：SQL
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次
输入表：
输出表：
加载策略：3 （注：1-全表覆盖 ，2-增量更新，3-增量追加）
创建时间：2024-11-20 15:09:10
创建人：zhangch2
修改历史：
版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明

***********************************************************/
delete from dw${env}.DWS_HR_YFXYYRGCBQK
where
    biz_year >= '2019';

insert into
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_YFXYYRGCBQK (
        `biz_year`,
        `biz_month`,
        `org_cn_abbr`,
        `org_cd`,
        `wages`
    )
SELECT
    data01.id_year as biz_year,
    cast(data01.id_period as char(10)) as biz_month,
    coalesce(data03.id_value, '') as org_name,
    data01.id_unitcode as org_code,
    0.0 + case
        when data01.sfzggzze_z is null
        or trim(data01.sfzggzze_z) = '' then 0
        else data01.sfzggzze_z
    end as wages
from
    (
        select
            id_unitcode,
            id_year,
            id_period,
            sfzggzze_z
        from
            (
                select distinct
                    id_unitcode,
                    id_periodtype,
                    id_year,
                    id_period,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'YBBC01201103220200'
                            and id_periodtype = 'Y' then id_value
                        end
                    ) sfzggzze_z
                from
                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_EFFICACY_INTF_DATA
                where
                    id_zbcode in ('YBBC01201103220200')
                    and id_periodtype = 'Y'
                    and id_value is not null
                    and id_value <> ''
                    and id_year = if (
                        month (now ()) = 1,
                        year (now ()) -1,
                        year (now ())
                    )
                    and id_unitcode in (
                        '1000009489',
                        '2016022439',
                        'WKHNYS00X9',
                        'WK030FZ029',
                        'WK050JR049',
                        'WK06000019',
                        'WKKYGLKJ09',
                        'YSWSYB0009',
                        'WK042CSK59',
                        '7389785319',
                        '7109358639',
                        '1017109172',
                        'ZGWKXG0039',
                        'MA00H7DA39',
                        'WKBJZCGL09',
                        '6985185729',
                        'WKKYGLKJ09'
                    )
            ) coll01
    ) data01
    join (
        select distinct
            id_unitcode,
            case
                when id_unitcode = '1000009489' then '中冶集团'
                when id_unitcode = '2016022439' then '五矿国际'
                when id_unitcode = 'WKHNYS00X9' then '湖南有色'
                when id_unitcode = 'WK030FZ029' then '五矿发展'
                when id_unitcode = 'WK050JR049' then '五矿资本'

        net_profit,
        gross_revenue,
        labor_cost,

        employees,
        mean_employees,
        total_productivity,
        workforce,
        employee_cost
    )
select
    data01.id_year as biz_year,

    data01.cyrypjrs_c as workforce,

from
    (
        select
            id_unitcode,
            id_year,
            ifnull (sum(qyrgcb_k + 0.0), 0) qyrgcb_k,
            ifnull (sum(zgrgcb_s + 0.0), 0) zgrgcb_s,
            ifnull (sum(zgzgpjrs_x + 0.0), 0) zgzgpjrs_x,
            ifnull (sum(jlr_u + 0.0), 0) jlr_u,
            ifnull (sum(yyzsr_e + 0.0), 0) yyzsr_e,
            ifnull (sum(yyzcb_z + 0.0), 0) yyzcb_z,
            ifnull (sum(cyrypjrs_c + 0.0), 0) cyrypjrs_c,
            ifnull (sum(lrze_f + 0.0), 0) lrze_f,
            ifnull (sum(ldsczz_e + 0.0), 0) ldsczz_e,
            ifnull (sum(zgrs_e + 0.0), 0) zgrs_e,
            ifnull (sum(sfzggzze_x + 0.0), 0) sfzggzze_x,
            ifnull (sum(zgpjrs_k + 0.0), 0) zgpjrs_k
        from

                select distinct

                    id_periodtype,
                    id_year,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080270'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) qyrgcb_k,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJCW20201700005'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) zgrgcb_s,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080060'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) zgzgpjrs_x,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF02201003080740'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value

                    ) jlr_u,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF02201003080010'

                        end
                    ) yyzsr_e,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF02201003080080'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) yyzcb_z,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080020'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) cyrypjrs_c,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF02201003080720'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) lrze_f,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_year <= '2021' then (
                                case
                                    when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080470'
                                    and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                                end
                            )
                            else (
                                case
                                    when id_zbcode = 'GJZF082022011'
                                    and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                                end
                            )
                        end
                    ) ldsczz_e,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080050'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) zgrs_e,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080280'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) sfzggzze_x,
                    (
                        case
                            when id_zbcode = 'GJZF08201003080050'
                            and id_periodtype = 'N' then id_value
                        end
                    ) zgpjrs_k
                from
                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_EFFICACY_INTF_DATA
                where
                    id_zbcode in (
                        'GJZF08201003080270',
                        'GJCW20201700005',
                        'GJZF08201003080060',
                        'GJZF02201003080740',
                        'GJZF02201003080010',

                        'GJZF08201003080470',
                        'GJZF08201003080050',
                        'GJZF082022011',
                        'GJZF08201003080280'
                    )
                    and id_periodtype = 'N'
                    and id_value is not null
                    and id_value <> ''
                    and id_unitcode in (
                        '10000093X9',
                        '1000009489',
                        '2016022439',
                        'WKHNYS00X9',
                        'WK030FZ029',
                        'WK050JR049',
                        'WK06000019',

任务名称：ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次
输入表：
输出表：

创建人：zhangch2
修改历史：
版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明

***********************************************************/
truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT;

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_COST_PROFIT (
        biz_year,
        org_cn_abbr,
        tot_cost,
        gross_prof,
        net_prof,
        biz_income,
        labor_cost,
        labor_cost_yoy,
        wages,
        wages_yoy,
        wrks,
        wages_per_cap,
        productivity,
        labor_cost_ratio,
        labor_cost_ratio_yoy,
        prof_mrgn,
        prof_mrgn_yoy,
        labor_prop,
        labor_prop_yoy,
        org_cd,
        biz_date
    )
with
    t as (
        select
            *,
            100 * labor_cost / gross_revenue as labor_cost_ratio, -- 人事费用率
            100 * gross_profit / labor_cost as prof_mrgn, -- 人工成本利润率
            100 * labor_cost / total_cost as labor_prop, -- 人工成本占总成本比例
            wages / mean_employees as wages_per_cap, -- 平均工资
            total_productivity / workforce as productivity -- 全员劳动生产率
        from
            dw${env}.DWS_HR_XYYRGCBQK
    )
select
    biz_year,
    org_cn_abbr,
    total_cost as tot_cost,
    gross_profit as gross_prof,
    net_profit as net_prof,
    gross_revenue as biz_income,
    labor_cost,
    100 * (
        labor_cost / lag (labor_cost, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_cn_abbr
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_cost_yoy,
    wages,
    100 * (
        wages / lag (wages, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_cn_abbr
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as wages_yoy,
    employees as wrks,
    wages_per_cap,
    productivity,
    labor_cost_ratio,
    100 * (
        labor_cost_ratio / lag (labor_cost_ratio, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_cn_abbr
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_cost_ratio_yoy,
    prof_mrgn,
    100 * (
        prof_mrgn / lag (prof_mrgn, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_cn_abbr
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as prof_mrgn_yoy,
    labor_prop,
    100 * (
        labor_prop / lag (labor_prop, 1, null) over (
            partition by
                org_cn_abbr
            order by
                biz_year
        ) - 1
    ) as labor_prop_yoy,
    org_cd,
    null as biz_date
from
    t

taskParams.sql:
truncate table dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ALERT_EXPIRY;

INSERT INTO
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ALERT_EXPIRY (
        alert_cat,
        a00,
        name,
        sex,
        birth_dt,
        age,
        org_cn_abbr,
        edu,
        `position`,
        ideo_pol
    )
select
    '近两年即将退休的干部' as alert_cat,
    a00,
    name,
    sex,
    birth_dt,
    timestampdiff (year, birth_dt, now ()) as age,
    org_cn_abbr,
    edu,
    `position`,
    ideo_pol
from
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER
where
    holds_position = 1
    and clsfn = '党组管干部'
    and current_status in ('在职', '挂职', '借调')
    and (
        (
            sex = '男'
            and year (now ()) - year (birth_dt) >= 58
        )
        or (
            sex = '女'
            and year (now ()) - year (birth_dt) >= 53
        )
    );

INSERT INTO
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ALERT_EXPIRY (
        alert_cat,
        a00,
        name,
        sex,
        birth_dt,
        age,
        org_cn_abbr,
        edu,
        `position`,
        ideo_pol,
        probation_dt
    )
select
    '试用期内的干部' as alert_cat,
    a00,
    name,
    sex,
    birth_dt,
    timestampdiff (year, birth_dt, now ()) as age,
    org_cn_abbr,
    edu,
    `position`,
    ideo_pol,
    probation_dt
from
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER
where
    holds_position = 1
    and clsfn = '党组管干部'
    and current_status in ('在职', '挂职', '借调')
    and probation_dt is not null
    and probation_result is null;

truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_EDU;

INSERT INTO ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_EDU
(`group`, edu, num_ppl, num_tot, biz_date)
with a as (
    select r.a00, path_abbr[3] as `group`, edu
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER as r inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p using (b00) 
    where holds_position = 1 and current_status = '在职' and clsfn = '党委管干部' and path_nm[2] = '直管企业'
    union all
    select a00, '党组管理干部' as `group`, edu
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER 
    where current_status in ('在职', '挂职', '借调') and clsfn = '党组管干部')
select 
    `group`,
    case 
        when edu like '%大学%' then '大学'
        when edu like '%博士%' then '博士研究生'
        when edu like '%研究生%' then '硕士研究生'
        else '其他'
    end as education,
    count(1) as num_ppl,
    sum(count(1)) over (partition by `group`) as num_tot,
    date_format(now(), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from a
group by `group`, education

taskParams.rawScript:
chmod +x ./duck.db
./duck.db << EOF

load './mysql_scanner.duckdb_extension';

create secret (
type mysql,
host '10.201.132.224',
port 9030,
user 'datakits_prod',
password 'cisdi@123456'
);

attach 'database=dw_prod' as dw_prod (type mysql);

with recursive tree(b00, org_cn_nm, org_cn_abbr, parent_b00, path_b00, path_nm, path_abbr) as (
select b00, b0101, b0104, zdyxb0114, [b00], [b0101], [b0104]
from dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_B01
where zdyxb0114 = '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
union all
select c.b00, c.b0101, c.b0104, zdyxb0114,
list_append(p.path_b00, c.b00),
list_append(p.path_nm, c.b0101),
list_append(p.path_abbr, c.b0104)
from dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_B01 as c inner join tree as p
on c.zdyxb0114 = p.b00)
insert into dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH by name
select *, strftime(current_date, '%Y%m%d') as biz_date
from tree;

EOF

taskParams.sql:
truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_AGE;

INSERT INTO ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_AGE
(`group`, division_type, age_group, num_ppl, num_tot, biz_date)
with a as (
    select r.a00, path_abbr[3] as `group`, timestampdiff (year, birth_dt, now ()) as age
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER as r inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p using (b00) 
    where holds_position = 1 and current_status = '在职' and clsfn = '党委管干部' and path_nm[2] = '直管企业'
    union all
    select a00, '党组管理干部' as `group`, timestampdiff (year, birth_dt, now ()) as age
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER 
    where current_status in ('在职', '挂职', '借调') and clsfn = '党组管干部'),
ag as (
    select *,
        '年龄分布' as division_type,
        case 
            when age >= 55 then '≥ 55'
            when age <= 46 then '≤ 46'
            else '47 - 55'
        end as age_group
    from a
    union all
    select *,
        '年龄结构' as division_type,
        case 
           when age >= 30 and age <= 35 then '30-35岁'
           when age >= 36 and age <= 40 then '36-40岁'
           when age >= 41 and age <= 45 then '41-45岁'
           when age >= 46 and age <= 50 then '46-50岁'
           when age >= 51 and age <= 55 then '51-55岁'
           when age >= 56 and age <= 60 then '56-60岁'
           else '其他'
        end as age_group
    from a)
select
    `group`, 
    division_type, 
    age_group, 
    count(1) as num_ppl,
    sum(count(1)) over (partition by `group`, division_type) as num_tot,
    date_format(now(), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from ag
group by `group`, division_type, age_group

truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_DEPUTY;

-- 直管企业专职党委副书记配置情况
INSERT INTO ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_DEPUTY
(org_cn_abbr, leadership, needed, detail, warn, biz_date)
with deputy as (  
  select p.path_abbr[3] as org_cn_abbr, `name`
  from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER as r inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A02 as a02 using(a00)
    inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p on a02.a0201b  = p.b00
  where p.path_abbr[2] = '直管企业' and p.path_abbr[4] = '党政领导班子、董监事会、纪委'  -- or p.b00 = '4E362FEB-78AE-EC3D-6B4F-FDC46793B232' 香港控股
    and a02.a0215b = 'T13B'  -- 职位：党委副书记 
    and a02.a0255 = '1' -- 任职状态：在任
    and a02.zdyxa0205 = '1'  -- 是否占职数：是
    and a02.zdyxa0284 = '1'),  -- 专职副书记
sz as (  -- 直管企业党委副书记设置情况
  select
    zgqy_w as org_cn_abbr,
    sfypzzdwfsj_r as needed
  from dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_ZGDWFSJSZQK
  where
    sfypzzdwfsj_r is not null)
select sz.org_cn_abbr, '专职党委副书记' as leadership, needed,
    if(needed = '是', ifnull(name, '应配未配'), '') as detail,
    '' as warn, date_format(now(), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from sz left join deputy using (org_cn_abbr);

    from dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_ZGDWFSJSZQK as sz 
        inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p on sz.zgqy_w = p.org_cn_abbr 
        inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_LDBZPZQKYJ as pz on pz.zzid_q = p.b00)

truncate table dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER;

INSERT INTO
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER (
        a00,
        b00,
        b00_list,
        identi_no,
        current_status,
        holds_position,
        name,
        org_cn_abbr,
        department,
        `position`,
        all_in_one,
        fulltime_deputy,
        birth_dt,
        sex,
        nat,
        ideo_pol,
        nat_place,
        hometown,
        ttl,
        start_work_dt,
        join_party_dt,
        probation_dt,
        probation_result,
        edu,
        diploma,
        univ,
        major,
        contact,
        clsfn,
        rmks,
        org_clsfn,
        position_clsfn,
        position_start,
        position_level,
        level_start,
        cadre_level,
        cadre_level_start,
        career_path,
        employee_level,
        employee_level_start,
        company_cadre_level_start,
        position_rotation_year_limit,
        level_rotation_year_limit,
        position_year_served,
        company_level_year_served,
        need_rotation,
        exp_hq,
        exp_ovrs,
        exp_out_bj,
        exp_basic,
        exp_frontline,
        exp_frontline_reg_pos,
        exp_org_reg_pos
    )
select
    upper(a01.a00) as a00,
    upper(any_value (b01.b00)) as b00,
    collect_list (upper(b01.b00)) as b00_list,
    any_value (a01.a0184) as identi_no, -- 身份证号
    any_value (hr23.dmcpt) as current_status, -- 人员现状 
    sum(a02f.a02_zairenzhiwu) > 0 as holds_position, -- 本单位是否有在任职务标识
    replace (any_value (a01.a0101), '　', '') as name, -- 姓名
    any_value (ifnull (b01.zdyxb0101, b0101)) as org_cn_abbr, -- 直管单位
    collect_list (b01.b0101) as department, -- 工作部门
    any_value (a01f.a02_a0215_all_rmb) as `position`, -- 职位
    if (any_value (hr164a.dmcpt) = '是', 1, 0) as all_in_one, -- 是否为一肩挑
    if (any_value (hr164.dmcpt) = '是', 1, 0) as fulltime_deputy, -- 是否为专职副书记
    any_value (date(a01.a0107)) as birth_dt, -- 出生日期
    any_value (gb22611.dmcpt) as sex, -- 性别
    any_value (gb3304.dmcpt) as nat, -- 民族
    any_value (gb4762.dmcpt) as ideo_pol, -- 政治面貌
    any_value (a01f.a01_a0111b_a0111a_rmb) as nat_place, -- 籍贯
    any_value (a01f.a01_a0114b_a0114a_rmb) as hometown, -- 出生地
    any_value (
        if (a01f.a06_a0601_rmb = '无', '', a01f.a06_a0601_rmb)
    ) as ttl, -- 职称
    any_value (date(a01.a0134)) as start_work_dt, -- 参工时间,
    any_value (date(a01f.a01_a0144_rmb)) as join_party_dt, -- 入党时间,
    any_value (date(a02.zdyxa0262)) as probation_date, -- 试用期满日期
    any_value (hr26.dmcpt) as probation_result, -- 试用期结果 
    any_value (a01f.a08_a0801) as edu, -- 学历
    any_value (a01f.a08_a0830) as diploma, -- 学位
    any_value (a01f.a08_a0806_zg) as univ, -- 毕业院校
    any_value (a01f.a08_a0809_zg) as major, -- 专业
    any_value (a01.zdyxa0145) as contact, -- 联系方式
    any_value (hr03.dmcpt) as clsfn, -- 干部管理类别
    any_value (a01.zdyxa0199) as rmks, -- 备注
    any_value (hr972.dmcpt) as org_clsfn, -- 单位类别
    any_value (hr973.dmcpt) as position_clsfn, -- 职务类别
    any_value (date(a01.zdyxa01s07)) as position_start, -- 任现职时间
    any_value (hr974.dmcpt) as position_level, -- 职务级别
    any_value (date(a01.zdyxa0282)) as level_start, -- 任现职务级别时间
    any_value (hr975.dmcpt) as cadre_level, -- 干部层级
    any_value (date(a01.zdyxa0286)) as cadre_level_start, -- 任现干部层级时间
    any_value (hr970.dmcpt) as career_path, -- 职位序列
    any_value (hr971.dmcpt) as employee_level, -- 员工职级,
    any_value (date(a01.zdyxa01s03)) as employee_level_start, -- 任现员工职级时间
    any_value (date(a49.a4940)) as company_cadre_level_start, -- 同企业现层级任职时间
    cast(any_value (a49.a4941) as int) as position_rotation_year_limit, -- 现岗位按规定需交流年限
    cast(any_value (a49.a4942) as int) as level_rotation_year_limit, -- 现层级按规定需交流年限
    cast(any_value (a49.a4943) as int) as position_year_served, -- 已在现岗位工作年限 
    cast(any_value (a49.a4944) as int) as company_level_year_served, -- 已在同一企业现层级工作年限
    if (any_value (hr164b.dmcpt) = '是', 1, 0) as need_rotation, -- 是否需交流
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = '3550660A-1408-45F3-B138-5E258370DDD9'
    ) > 0 as exp_hq, -- 集团总部经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = '3C30020E-20ED-454D-B06C-1C7E405F37C6'
    ) > 0 as exp_ovrs, -- 海外工作经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = '483EF7DE-1A70-442B-B247-08DE63A4238B'
    ) > 0 as exp_out_bj, -- 京外工作经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = '5E111D02-F009-44FF-9890-A595A497A4C4'
    ) > 0 as exp_basic, -- 基层工作经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = 'F6657E73-9782-4F75-904C-B4289E5CDC96'
    ) > 0 as exp_frontline, -- 一线企业经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = 'CE773A9B-192B-4AEC-90DA-CBD3E28ACCAD'
    ) > 0 as exp_frontline_reg_pos, -- 一线企业正职经历
    sum(
        coalesce(jmark.dmcod, '') = 'AA6FC965-B6A0-43F7-AFE2-55A7156F0B7C'
    ) > 0 as exp_org_reg_pos -- 直管企业内设机构正职经历
from
    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A01 as a01
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A02 as a02 on upper(a01.a00) = upper(a02.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A02_FUNCTION as a02f on upper(a01.a00) = upper(a02f.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A01_FUNCTION as a01f on upper(a01.a00) = upper(a01f.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_B01 as b01 on upper(b01.b00) = upper(a02f.a0201b)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A06 as a06 on upper(a01.a00) = upper(a06.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A01_JLMARK_R as jmark on upper(a01.a00) = upper(jmark.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADRE_A49 as a49 on upper(a01.a00) = upper(a49.a00)
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR03 as hr03 on a01.zdyxa0110 = hr03.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_GB3304 as gb3304 on gb3304.dmcod = a01.a0117
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_GB22611 as gb22611 on gb22611.dmcod = a01.a0104
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_GB4762 as gb4762 on gb4762.dmcod = a01.a0141
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR970 as hr970 on a01.zdyxa01s01 = hr970.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR971 as hr971 on a01.zdyxa01s02 = hr971.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR973 as hr973 on a01.a0219 = hr973.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR974 as hr974 on a01.zdyxa0281 = hr974.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR972 as hr972 on a01.zdyxa0287 = hr972.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR975 as hr975 on a01.zdyxa0285 = hr975.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR164A as hr164a on a02.zdyxa0283 = hr164a.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR164 as hr164 on a02.zdyxa0284 = hr164.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR164 as hr164b on a49.a4945 = hr164b.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR26 as hr26 on a02.zdyxa0217 = hr26.dmcod
    left join dw${env}.DIM_HR_CADRE_HR23 as hr23 on a01.zdyxa0109 = hr23.dmcod
where
    ifnull (a02.zdyxa0288, 0) = 0
    and ifnull (a01.delflag, '0') != '1'
group by
    a01.a00

truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_EXPERIENCE;

INSERT INTO ads${env}.ADS_HR_CADRE_EXPERIENCE
(`group`, `exp`, num_ppl, biz_date)
with r as (
    select *, array(
        concat('集团总部经历,', exp_hq),
        concat('海外工作经历,', exp_ovrs),
        concat('京外工作经历,', exp_out_bj),
        concat('基层工作经历,', exp_basic),
        concat('一线企业经历,', exp_frontline),
        concat('一线企业正职经历,', exp_frontline_reg_pos),
        concat('直管企业内设机构正职经历,', exp_org_reg_pos)
        ) as exps
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_ROSTER),
e as (
    select r.a00, path_abbr[3] as `group`, exps
    from r inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p using (b00) 
    where holds_position = 1 and current_status = '在职' and clsfn = '党委管干部' and path_nm[2] = '直管企业'
    union all
    select a00, '党组管理干部' as `group`, exps
    from r
    where holds_position = 1 and current_status in ('在职', '挂职', '借调') and clsfn = '党组管干部'),
ex as (
    select a00, `group`, 
        split_part(ex, ',', 1) as `exp`, 
        cast(split_part(ex, ',', 2) as boolean) as val
    from e lateral view explode(exps) t as ex)
select `group`, `exp`, sum(val) as num_ppl, date_format(now(), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from ex
group by `group`, `exp`

truncate table dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_TEAM;

INSERT INTO dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_TEAM
(b00, team, org_cat, org_cn_abbr, biz_date, positions, allocated, members)
with ldbz as (
    select b00, path_abbr[2] as org_cat, path_abbr[3] as org_cn, l.*
    from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_LDBZPZQKYJ as l  
        inner join dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADRE_B00_PATH as p on l.bmid_f = p.b00
    where case 
        when path_abbr[2] = '总部部门' then path_abbr[4] = '领导班子'
        when path_abbr[3] = '中冶集团' then path_abbr[5] = '60022018'
        else path_abbr[4] in ('党政领导班子、董监事会、纪委', '领导班子') end),
team as (
    select b00, '党政班子' as team, org_cat, org_cn,
        dzbzzzs_q as positions, dzbzsps_h as allocated, dzbzrypz_c as members
    from ldbz
    union all
    select b00, '董事会班子' as team, org_cat, org_cn,
        dshbzzzs_j as positions, dshbzsps_h as allocated, dshbzrypz_v as members
    from ldbz where org_cat = '直管企业'
    union all
    select b00, '党委班子' as team, org_cat, org_cn, 
        dwbzzzs_m as positions, dwbzsps_s as allocated, dwbzrypz_m as members
    from ldbz where org_cat = '直管企业'
    union all
    select b00, '经理层班子' as team, org_cat, org_cn,
        jlcbzzzs_g as positions, jlcbzsps_h as allocated, jlcbzrypz_l as members
    from ldbz where org_cat = '直管企业')
select b00, team, org_cat, org_cn, date_format (now (), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date, positions, allocated, members
from team

任务名称：SQL
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次

delete from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADSUP_ASSESS_SINGLE
where
    import_type = '同步';

INSERT INTO
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADSUP_ASSESS_SINGLE (
        id,
        biz_year,
        org_cn_abbr,
        org_cd,
        import_type,
        topic,
        num_ppl,
        choice_a,
        choice_b,
        choice_c,
        choice_uninformed,
        choice_abstain,
        biz_date
    )
with
    survey as (
        select
            a.survey_id,
            b.qu_id,
            b.qu_name,
            e.quo_id,
            a.org_code,
            c.asg_organname,
            a.`year`,
            d.t_sum,
            e.quo_order,
            e.quo_name,
            c.asg_organcode
        from
            (
                select
                    survey_id,
                    count(1) as t_sum
                from
                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS
                where
                    status = 1
                group by
                    survey_id
            ) as d
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY as a using (survey_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION as b using (survey_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION_OPTION as e using (qu_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_ASS_HRTREE_GXB as c on a.org_code = c.asg_organcode
        where
            a.examine = 1
            and b.qu_type = 0
    ),
    percent as (
        select
            f.survey_id,
            c.quo_id,
            count(c.quo_id) as choicenum,
            count(c.quo_id) / g.t_sum as percent,
            c.quo_order as quoorder
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION as b
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION_OPTION as c using (qu_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_ANSWER as d using (quo_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS as e using (survey_id)
            inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY as f using (survey_id)
            inner join (
                select
                    b.`year`,
                    b.org_code,
                    count(a.tss_id) as t_sum
                from
                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS as a
                    inner join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY as b using (survey_id)
                where
                    a.status = 1
                    and b.examine = 1
                    and b.year is not null
                    and b.org_code is not null
                    and b.year != ''
                    and b.org_code != ''
                group by
                    b.`year`,
                    b.org_code
            ) as g using (org_code, `year`)
        where
            b.qu_type = 0
            and e.status = 1
        group by
            f.survey_id,
            b.qu_name,
            c.quo_id,
            b.qu_order,
            c.quo_order,
            g.t_sum
    )
select
    uuid () as id,
    `year` as biz_year,
    case
        when asg_organname in ('五矿资本控股有限公司', '五矿资本股份有限公司') then '五矿资本股份有限公司'
        else asg_organname
    end as org_cn_abbr,
    any_value (asg_organcode) as org_cd,
    '同步' as import_type,
    qu_name as topic,
    t_sum as num_ppl,
    sum(
        case
            when quo_order = 1 then ifnull (percent, 0)
            else 0
        end
    ) as choice_a,
    sum(
        case
            when quo_order = 2 then ifnull (percent, 0)
            else 0
        end
    ) as choice_b,
    sum(
        case
            when quo_order = 3 then ifnull (percent, 0)
            else 0
        end
    ) as choice_c,
    sum(
        case
            when quo_order = 4 then ifnull (percent, 0)
            else 0
        end
    ) as choice_uninformed,
    0 as choice_abstain,
    date_format (now (), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from
    survey
    left join percent using (survey_id, quo_id)
where
    org_code in (
        '60003375',
        '60007665',
        '60000011',
        '60000031',
        '60014009',
        '70000003',
        '60021506',
        '60002658',
        '60023084',
        '60000170',
        '60022729',
        '60003661',
        '60000017',
        '60000200',
        '60002617',
        '60003054'
    )
group by
    `year`,
    qu_name,
    org_code,
    asg_organname,
    t_sum;

delete from dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADSUP_ASSESS_MULTIPLE
where
    import_type = '同步';

INSERT INTO
    dw${env}.DWS_HR_CADSUP_ASSESS_MULTIPLE (
        id,
        record_dt,
        biz_year,
        import_type,
        org_cn_nm,
        org_cd,
        topic,
        num_ppl,
        indictr,
        matchup,
        biz_date
    )
with
    surveydata as (
        select
            a.survey_id,
            b.qu_id,
            a.org_code,
            b.qu_name,
            d.quo_id,
            d.quo_name,
            c.asg_organname,
            a.year,
            any_value (c.asg_organcode) as asg_organcode
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY a
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION b using (survey_id)
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_ASS_HRTREE_GXB c on a.org_code = c.asg_organcode
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION_OPTION d on b.qu_id = d.qu_id
        where
            a.examine = 1
            and b.qu_type = 1
        group by
            b.qu_id,
            b.qu_name,
            a.org_code,
            c.asg_organname,
            a.year,
            a.survey_id,
            b.qu_order,
            d.quo_id,
            d.quo_name,
            d.quo_order
    ),
    answerdata as (
        select
            g.survey_id,
            f.qu_id as f_qu_id,
            c.quo_name as quname,
            count(c.quo_id) as choicenum,
            cast(count(c.quo_id) / r.t_sum * 100 as decimal(10, 2)) as percent,
            c.quo_order as quo_order,
            c.quo_id as c_quo_id
        from
            (
                select
                    count(a.tss_id) as t_sum,
                    a.survey_id
                from
                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS a
                    join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY b on a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                where
                    a.status = 1
                    and b.examine = 1
                    and b.org_code is not null
                    and b.org_code != ''
                    and b.year is not null
                    and b.year != ''
                group by
                    a.survey_id
            ) r
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY g on g.survey_id = r.survey_id
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS e on e.survey_id = g.survey_id
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION f on f.qu_type = 1
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION_OPTION c on f.qu_id = c.qu_id
            join dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_ANSWER d on e.tss_id = d.tss_id
            and d.quo_id = c.quo_id
        where
            g.examine = 1
            and e.status = 1
        group by
            g.survey_id,
            f.qu_id,
            c.quo_id,
            c.quo_name,
            c.quo_order,
            r.t_sum
    )
select
    uuid () as ids,
    current_date() as record_dt,
    year as biz_year,
    '同步' as import_type,
    case
        when asg_organname = '五矿资本控股有限公司' then '五矿资本股份有限公司'
        when asg_organname = '五矿资本股份有限公司' then '五矿资本股份有限公司'
        else asg_organname
    end as org_cn_nm,
    asg_organcode as org_cd,
    quo_name as topic,
    ifnull (choicenum, 0) as num_ppl,
    ifnull (percent, 0) as indictr,
    case
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 3) = '（12' then '12'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 3) = '（11' then '11'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑩'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 3) = '（10' then '10'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '①'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（1' then '1'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '②'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（2' then '2'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '③'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（3' then '3'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '④'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（4' then '4'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑤'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（5' then '5'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑥'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（6' then '6'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑦'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（7' then '7'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑧'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（8' then '8'
        when substr (quo_name, 1, 1) = '⑨'
        or substr (quo_name, 1, 2) = '（9' then '9'
        else '0'
    end as matchup,
    date_format (now (), 'yyyyMMdd') as biz_date
from
    (
        select
            a.*,
            b.choicenum,
            b.percent
        from
            surveydata a
            left join answerdata b on a.survey_id = b.survey_id
            and a.qu_id = b.f_qu_id
            and a.quo_id = b.c_quo_id
    ) rl_ybglpydxkftbjg_xx
where
    org_code in (
        '60003375',
        '60007665',
        '60000011',
        '60000031',
        '60014009',
        '70000003',
        '60021506',
        '60002658',
        '60023084',
        '60000170',
        '60022729',
        '60003661',
        '60000017',
        '60000200',
        '60002617',
        '60003054'
    );

    jbrt_u as jbrt,
    brt_a as brt,
    blj_u as blj,
    qq_i as qq
from
    (
        select distinct
            gbxb.*
        from
            (
                select
                    *
                from
                    (
                        select
                            asg_organcode,
                            asg_organname,
                            year,
                            quo_id,
                            sum(
                                case
                                    when quoidbtn = 0 then ifnull (percent, 0)
                                    else 0
                                end
                            ) as rt_w,
                            sum(
                                case
                                    when quoidbtn = 1 then ifnull (percent, 0)
                                    else 0
                                end
                            ) as jbrt_u,
                            sum(
                                case
                                    when quoidbtn = 2 then ifnull (percent, 0)
                                    else 0
                                end
                            ) as brt_a,
                            sum(
                                case
                                    when quoidbtn = 3 then ifnull (percent, 0)
                                    else 0
                                end
                            ) as blj_u,
                            0.0 as qq_i,
                            xxbgbxx.qu_id
                        from
                            (
                                select
                                    a.survey_id,
                                    a.survey_name,
                                    a.asg_organcode,
                                    a.asg_organname,
                                    a.year,
                                    a.qu_id,
                                    a.qu_name,
                                    a.table_datatits,
                                    a.table_data,
                                    a.table_btns,
                                    b.quo_id,
                                    b.percent,
                                    b.choicenum,
                                    b.t_sum,
                                    b.quoidbtn
                                from
                                    (
                                        select
                                            a.survey_id,
                                            a.survey_name,
                                            c.asg_organcode,
                                            c.asg_organname,
                                            a.year,
                                            b.qu_id,
                                            b.qu_name,
                                            b.table_datatits,
                                            b.table_data,
                                            b.table_btns
                                        from
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY a,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION b,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_ASS_HRTREE_GXB c
                                        where
                                            a.org_code = c.asg_organcode
                                            and a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                            and a.examine = 1
                                            and b.qu_type = 7
                                            and b.table_datatits not like '%身份证%'
                                        group by
                                            a.survey_id,
                                            a.survey_name,
                                            c.asg_organcode,
                                            c.asg_organname,
                                            a.year,
                                            b.qu_id,
                                            b.qu_name,
                                            b.table_datatits,
                                            b.table_data,
                                            b.table_btns
                                    ) a,
                                    (
                                        select
                                            convert(
                                                count(a.quo_id_btn) / f.t_sum * 100,
                                                decimal(10, 2)
                                            ) percent,
                                            count(a.quo_id_btn) as choicenum,
                                            f.t_sum,
                                            a.quo_id_btn as quoidbtn,
                                            a.quo_id,
                                            c.survey_id,
                                            d.qu_id
                                        from
                                            (
                                                select
                                                    count(a.tss_id) as t_sum,
                                                    b.survey_id
                                                from
                                                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS a,
                                                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY b
                                                where
                                                    a.`status` = 1
                                                    and b.year is not null
                                                    and b.year != ''
                                                    and b.org_code is not null
                                                    and b.org_code != ''
                                                    and a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                                    and b.examine = 1
                                                group by
                                                    b.survey_id
                                            ) f,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_ANSWER a,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS b,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY c,
                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION d
                                        where
                                            a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                            and a.survey_id = c.survey_id
                                            and c.survey_id = f.survey_id
                                            and b.`status` = 1
                                            and b.tss_id = a.tss_id
                                            and a.qu_id = d.qu_id
                                            and d.qu_type = 7
                                            and d.table_datatits not like '%身份证%'
                                        group by
                                            c.survey_id,
                                            d.qu_id,
                                            a.quo_id,
                                            a.quo_id_btn,
                                            f.t_sum
                                    ) b
                                where
                                    a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                    and a.qu_id = b.qu_id
                            ) xxbgbxx
                        group by
                            asg_organcode,
                            asg_organname,
                            year,
                            quo_id,
                            qu_id
                    ) rl_xtbgbmzpyjg
                    join (
                        select
                            (
                                case
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[0].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."0"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[1].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."1"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[2].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."2"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[3].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."3"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[4].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."4"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[5].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."5"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[6].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."6"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[7].con')) = '姓名' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."7"')
                                    )
                                    else ''
                                end
                            ) as 姓名,
                            (
                                case
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[0].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."0"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[1].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."1"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[2].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."2"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[3].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."3"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[4].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."4"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[5].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."5"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[6].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."6"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[7].con')) = '出生年月' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."7"')
                                    )
                                    else ''
                                end
                            ) as 出生年月,
                            (
                                case
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[0].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."0"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[1].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."1"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[2].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."2"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[3].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."3"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[4].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."4"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[5].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."5"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[6].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."6"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[7].con')) = '原任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."7"')
                                    )
                                    else ''
                                end
                            ) as 原任职务,
                            (
                                case
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[0].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."0"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[1].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."1"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[2].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."2"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[3].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."3"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[4].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."4"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[5].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."5"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[6].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."6"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[7].con')) = '现任职务' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."7"')
                                    )
                                    else ''
                                end
                            ) as 现任职务,
                            (
                                case
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[0].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."0"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[1].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."1"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[2].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."2"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[3].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."3"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[4].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."4"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[5].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."5"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[6].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."6"')
                                    )
                                    when json_unquote (json_extract (table_datatits,'$[7].con')) = '任现任职务时间' then json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."7"')
                                    )
                                    else ''
                                end
                            ) as 任职时间,
                            json_unquote (
                                json_extract (replace (table_data, "\n", ""), '$."id"')
                            ) as 问题id,
                            qu_id1
                        from
                            (
                                select
                                    json_unquote (
                                        json_extract (
                                            table_data,
                                            concat ('$[', help_topic.help_topic_id, ']')
                                        )
                                    ) as table_data,
                                    table_datatits,
                                    table_datas.qu_id as qu_id1
                                from
                                    (
                                        select
                                            table_data,
                                            table_datatits,
                                            gbxx.qu_id
                                        from
                                            (
                                                select
                                                    a.survey_id,
                                                    a.survey_name,
                                                    a.asg_organcode,
                                                    a.asg_organname,
                                                    a.year,
                                                    a.qu_id,
                                                    a.qu_name,
                                                    a.table_datatits,
                                                    a.table_data,
                                                    a.table_btns,
                                                    b.quo_id,
                                                    b.percent,
                                                    b.choicenum,
                                                    b.t_sum,
                                                    b.quoidbtn
                                                from
                                                    (
                                                        select
                                                            a.survey_id,
                                                            a.survey_name,
                                                            c.asg_organcode,
                                                            c.asg_organname,
                                                            a.year,
                                                            b.qu_id,
                                                            b.qu_name,
                                                            b.table_datatits,
                                                            b.table_data,
                                                            b.table_btns
                                                        from
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY a,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION b,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_ASS_HRTREE_GXB c
                                                        where
                                                            a.org_code = c.asg_organcode
                                                            and a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                                            and a.examine = 1
                                                            and b.qu_type = 7
                                                            and b.table_datatits not like '%身份证%'
                                                        group by
                                                            a.survey_id,
                                                            a.survey_name,
                                                            c.asg_organcode,
                                                            c.asg_organname,
                                                            a.year,
                                                            b.qu_id,
                                                            b.qu_name,
                                                            b.table_datatits,
                                                            b.table_data,
                                                            b.table_btns
                                                    ) a,
                                                    (
                                                        select
                                                            convert(
                                                                count(a.quo_id_btn) / f.t_sum * 100,
                                                                decimal(10, 2)
                                                            ) percent,
                                                            count(a.quo_id_btn) as choicenum,
                                                            f.t_sum,
                                                            a.quo_id_btn as quoidbtn,
                                                            a.quo_id,
                                                            c.survey_id,
                                                            d.qu_id
                                                        from
                                                            (
                                                                select
                                                                    count(a.tss_id) as t_sum,
                                                                    b.survey_id
                                                                from
                                                                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS a,
                                                                    dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY b
                                                                where
                                                                    a.`status` = 1
                                                                    and b.year is not null
                                                                    and b.year != ''
                                                                    and b.org_code is not null
                                                                    and b.org_code != ''
                                                                    and a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                                                    and b.examine = 1
                                                                group by
                                                                    b.survey_id
                                                            ) f,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_ANSWER a,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_STATUS b,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_SURVEY_DIRECTORY c,
                                                            dw${env}.DWD_HR_CADSUP_QUESTION d
                                                        where
                                                            a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                                            and a.survey_id = c.survey_id
                                                            and c.survey_id = f.survey_id
                                                            and b.`status` = 1
                                                            and b.tss_id = a.tss_id
                                                            and a.qu_id = d.qu_id
                                                            and d.qu_type = 7
                                                            and d.table_datatits not like '%身份证%'
                                                        group by
                                                            c.survey_id,
                                                            d.qu_id,
                                                            a.quo_id,
                                                            a.quo_id_btn,
                                                            f.t_sum
                                                    ) b
                                                where
                                                    a.survey_id = b.survey_id
                                                    and a.qu_id = b.qu_id
                                            ) gbxx
                                    ) table_datas
                                    join dw${env}.DIM_MYSQL_HELP_TOPIC as help_topic on help_topic.help_topic_id
<json_length (table_data)
                                where
                                    json_valid (table_data) > 0
                                    and json_length (table_data) > 0
                            ) jsons
                    ) gbxx_data on rl_xtbgbmzpyjg.quo_id = gbxx_data.问题id
                    and rl_xtbgbmzpyjg.qu_id = gbxx_data.qu_id1
                where
                    asg_organcode in (
                        '60003375',
                        '60007665',
                        '60000011',
                        '60000031',
                        '60014009',
                        '70000003',
                        '60021506',
                        '60002658',
                        '60023084',
                        '60000170',
                        '60022729',
                        '60003661',
                        '60000017',
                        '60000200',
                        '60002617',
                        '60003054'
                    )
            ) gbxb
    ) gbxb_tb

/***********************************************************
任务名称：ADS_HR_TALENT_OVERV_DUTY
功能描述：
运行频率：每 N 分钟/小时/天 一次
输入表：
输出表：
加载策略：3 （注：1-全表覆盖 ，2-增量更新，3-增量追加）
创建时间：2024-12-17 10:39:23
创建人：zhaojl6
修改历史：
版本          更改日期          更改人             修改说明

***********************************************************/
truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_TALENT_OVERV_DUTY;

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_TALENT_OVERV_DUTY
SELECT
    id,
    m.org_cd as org_cd,
    unit_name as org_cn_abbr,
    YEAR (statis_date) as biz_year,
    active_empl_num as num,
    now () as etl_time
from
    dw${env}.DWD_HR_PERSON_OVERV o
    left join (
        SELECT
            *
        from
            (
                SELECT
                    org_cd,
                    org_cn_abbr,
                    row_number() over (
                        partition by
                            org_cn_abbr
                        order by
                            org_cd
                    ) as rank
                from
                    dw${env}.DIM_ORG_MAP
                where
                    biz = '人才管理'
            ) a
        where
            a.rank = 1
    ) m on o.unit_name = m.org_cn_abbr
where
    unit_name != '集团总部'
order by
    sort_num

SELECT
    uuid () as id,
    '首席技师' as grade,
    prof_field,
    name,
    photo,
    gender,
    birth_date as birth,
    polit_status as Poli_status,

    job_type as career,
    null as is_less_5_year,
    now () as elt_time

    dw${env}.DWD_HR_SKILL_TALENT_STRU_FIR
union all
SELECT
    uuid () as id,
    '特级技师' as grade,
    prof_field,
    name,
    null as photo,
    gender,
    birth_date as birth,
    polit_status as Poli_status,
    direct_manage_comp as unit,
    job_type as career,
    if (
        TimeStampDiff (
            year,
            DATE_SUB (
                LAST_DAY (
                    DATE_ADD (NOW (), INTERVAL 12 - MONTH (NOW ()) MONTH)
                ),
                INTERVAL 1 YEAR
            ),
            DATE_ADD (birth_date, INTERVAL 60 YEAR)
        )
<5,
        '是',
        ''
    ) as is_less_5_year,

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_TALENT_ALERT
SELECT
    id,
    reason,
    num_ppl,
    detail,
    etl_time
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            uuid () as id,
            '国家重点实验室高层次人才数量不足' as reason,
            COUNT(1) num_ppl,
            CONCAT (
                '{',
                GROUP_CONCAT (
                    json_array (
                        id,
                        gjzdsys,
                        ytdw,
                        ndkjrczs,
                        ndgcckjrcsl,
                        gccrczb,
                        ndbdwkjrcsl,
                        ndbdwgzrs,
                        sndbdwkjrcsl,
                        sndbdwgzrs,
                        jl
                    )
                ),
                '}'
            ) detail,
            now () as etl_time
        FROM
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_GJZDSYSGCCRCSLBZ
        WHERE
            JL = '高层次人才占比不足'
        UNION ALL
        SELECT
            uuid () as id,
            '三级以上企业高层次科技人才减少企业' as reason,
            COUNT(1) num_ppl,
            CONCAT (
                '{',
                GROUP_CONCAT (
                    json_array (id, qym, ndgcckjrcsl, syndgcckjrcsl, zl)
                ),
                '}'
            ) detail,
            now () as etl_time
        FROM
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_SJYJQYGCCKJRCJSQYS
        WHERE
            ZL
<0
        UNION ALL
        SELECT
            uuid () as id,
            '直管企业中高层次科技人才存在年龄结构风险企业' as reason,
            sum(
                case
                    when zb > 0.33
                    and qym != '全集团' then 1
                    else 0
                end
            ) num_ppl,
            CONCAT ('{', GROUP_CONCAT (json_array (id, qym, zb)), '}') as detail,
            now () as etl_time
        FROM
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_ZGQYZGCCKJRCCZNLJGFXQYS
        where
            qym != '全集团'
        UNION ALL
        SELECT
            uuid () as id,
            '直管企业中暂无高层次科技人才企业' as reason,
            COUNT(1) num_ppl,
            CONCAT (
                '{',
                GROUP_CONCAT (json_array (id, qym, bndgcckjrcsl)),
                '}'
            ) as detail,
            now () as etl_time
        FROM
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_ZGQYZZWGCKJRCQYS
        WHERE
            BNDGCCKJRCSL <= 0
    ) T;

truncate table ads${env}.ADS_HR_SKILL_TALENT_TEAM_LEVEL;

insert into
    ads${env}.ADS_HR_SKILL_TALENT_TEAM_LEVEL
SELECT
    uuid () as id,
    a.direct_manage_comp,
    null as org_cd,
    a.project as grade,
    a.pro_total as number,
    a.pro_total / b.total as prop,
    c.pro_total / a.pro_total as rtrm_prop,
    now () as etl_time
from
    (
        SELECT
            direct_manage_comp,
            project,
            sum(number) pro_total
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_SKILL_TALENT_OVERV
        where
            project in (
                '普通工',
                '五级岗位（初级工）',
                '四级岗位（中级工）',
                '三级岗位（高级工）',
                '二级岗位（技师）',
                '一级岗位（高级技师）'
            )
        group by
            direct_manage_comp,
            project
    ) a
    left join (
        SELECT
            direct_manage_comp,
            sum(number) as total
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_SKILL_TALENT_OVERV
        group by
            direct_manage_comp
    ) b on a.direct_manage_comp = b.direct_manage_comp
    left join (
        SELECT
            direct_manage_comp,
            project,
            sum(number) pro_total
        from
            dw${env}.DWD_HR_SKILL_TALENT_OVERV
        where
            project in (
                '普通工',
                '五级岗位（初级工）',
                '四级岗位（中级工）',
                '三级岗位（高级工）',
                '二级岗位（技师）',
                '一级岗位（高级技师）'
            )
            and type in ('55岁至59岁', '60岁及以上')
        group by
            direct_manage_comp,
            project
    ) c on a.direct_manage_comp = c.direct_manage_comp
    and a.project = c.project

truncate table dw${env}.DWD_HR_ZYGZPJQSXQ;

insert into
    dw${env}.DWD_HR_ZYGZPJQSXQ
SELECT
    z.*,
    m.org_cd,
    m.org_cn_nm,
    m.org_cn_abbr,
    now () as etl_time
from
    ods${env}.ODS_DAE01_ZYGZPJQSXQ z
    left join (
        select
            *
        from
            dw${env}.DIM_ORG_MAP
        where
            m.biz = '人才管理'
    ) m on z.zgqy = m.biz_name;
